# UI Design

Follow `docs/policy/ui-policy.md` for the full design system. Key rules:

- Use semantic color tokens (`bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`), never raw oklch/hex in components
- See `docs/policy/color-policy.md` for OKLCH chroma ranges, contrast requirements, and dark mode
- See `docs/policy/diagram-policy.md` for Mermaid diagram styling and authoring
- Opacity modifiers: `bg-neutral/30`, `border-border/50` (range 5-90, steps of 10)
- Typography: Geist Sans (UI), Geist Mono (code); body 16px, code 14px, min 12px
- Use `cn()` for class merging, `cva` for variants, `data-slot` for compound components
- No inline `style=` for colors, spacing, or typography — use Tailwind classes
- Animation: max 500ms, only animate `transform` and `opacity`, honor `prefers-reduced-motion`
